<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>클라이언트-서버 인터랙션 데모</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>클라이언트-서버 요청 실습</h1>

  <h2>1. GET 요청 (제출)</h2>
  <form action="/search" method="get">
    값 1: <input type="text" name="value1" placeholder="예: 사과"><br>
    값 2: <input type="text" name="value2" placeholder="예: 바나나"><br>
    <button>제출</button>
  </form>

<h2>2. POST 요청 (댓글 작성)</h2>
<form action="/submit-form" method="post">
  숫자 1: <input type="number" name="value1"><br>
  숫자 2: <input type="number" name="value2"><br>
  <button>POST 요청 보내기</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>
